課程教材 Course Material
	    Jia-ming Liu, “Photonic Devices,” Cambridge University Press (2009)    

參考書目 References
	    1. Amnon Yariv and Pochi Yeh, “Photonics, 6th edition”, Oxford University Press (2007)
2. B. E. A. Saleh and M. C. Teich, “Fundamental of Photonics, 2nd ed.”, John Wiley & Sons (2007)    

備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 具備專業倫理、社會責任、人文涵養與國際視野
 Possession of professional ethics, social responsibility, humanity and culture , and global vision
 

核心能力 Competence
■ 具備基礎科學(數學、物理、化學)與光電科學與工程的知識
 Possession of knowledge in fundamental science (mathematics, physics, chemistry) and photonics
■ 辨識與規劃解決光電科學與工程問題的能力
 Capability to identify and solve photonic problems and issues
□ 設計與執行光電實驗與工程實務的能力
 Capability to design and conduct photonic experiments and engineering practices
■ 分析與解釋光電相關現象與效應的能力
 Capability to analyze and explain photonic phenomena and effects
■ 整合光電、物理、化學、材料與電機等跨領域的能力
 Capability for interdisciplinary integration among photonics, physics, chemistry, materials, and electrical engineering
□ 具備有效的溝通能力，以及團隊合作的精神
 Capability for effective communication and team work
■ 掌握科學與社會發展，並擁有獨自與持續學習的能力
 Capability to catch up with science and social developments, and to learn independently and continuously
□ 增強外文能力
 Improvement in foreign languages
 

課程概述 Course Description
       Introducing the concept and applications of light wave propagation, generation, controlling and detection. 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
具備基礎科學(數學、物理、化學)與光電科學與工程的相關知識辨識與規劃解決光電科學與工程問題的能力分析與解釋光電相關現象與效應的能力擁有雷射技術，聲光、電光調製技術的相關知識 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction and Chapter6：Electro-optic devices2Chapter6：Electro-optic devices3Chapter 8: Acousto-optic devices4Chapter 8: Acousto-optic devices5Chapter 10: Laser amplifiers6Chapter 10: Laser amplifiers7清明節與兒童節(放假乙次)8Chapter 10: Laser amplifiers9Chapter 11: Laser oscillators10Chapter 11: Laser oscillators11Midterm Examination 212Chapter 12: Semiconductor basics13Chapter 12: Semiconductor basics14Chapter 13: Semiconductor lasers and light-emitting diodes15Chapter 13: Semiconductor lasers and light-emitting diodes16Chapter 14: Photodetectors17Chapter 14: Photodetectors18Final Examination 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


