* 連結如有失效，請來信告知！



　
 資格考參考書籍 以下書籍及範圍僅供參考。




一、光電子學 
1. 考試範圍：
 
光電子學I範圍
Chap 1 Ray Optics
 
Chap 2 Wave Optics
 
Chap 3 Beam Optics
 
Chap 4 Fourier Optics
 
Chap 5 Electromagnetic Optics
 
Chap 6 Polarization Optics
 
Chap 10 Resonator Optics
 
Chap 11 Statistical Optics (only 11.1,11.2)
 
Chap 12 Photon Optics (only 12.1)
 
光電子學 II範圍
 
Chap 8 Guided-wave Optics
 
Chap 9 Fiber Optics
 
Chap 13 Photons and Atoms
 
Chap 14 Laser Amplifier
 
Chap 15 Lasers
 
Chap 16 Semiconductor Optics
 
Chap 17 Semiconductor Photon Sources
 
Chap 20 Electro-Optics
 
Chap 21 Nonlinear Optics

2. 參考書目：
“Fundamentals of Photonics” by Saleh and Teich


二、電磁理論
1. 考試範圍：
Electrostatics, Magnetostatics, Boundary Value Problems, Maxwell Equations, Plane wave, Transmission line and Waveguides.
2. 參考書目：
（1）”Field and Wave Electromagnetics” by David Cheng
（2） “Field and Waves in Communication Electronics” by S. Ramo, J. Whinnery and T. Van Duzer
 







